These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, artichoke, nectarine, grapes, broccoli, grapefruit, lemon
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, ritmeester, pall-mall, alhambra, vegafina, dannemann, dunhill
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating lemon##1
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
 5. the person eating pear is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 9. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
10. the person eating grapes is the ritmeester-smoker##1
11. the person eating grapes is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person eating nectarine##2
12. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Food   | grapefruit  | grapes | nectarine  | broccoli | pear | artichoke | lemon |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | ritmeester   | dunhill | alhambra  | dannemann   | vegafina    | aristoff    |

