.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
City: liverpool, colone, berlin, boston, miami, rome, nizza
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, ambient, pop, dubstep, hip-hop, classical, d&b
 1. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the fan of classical is in the middle##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 8. the person traveling to boston is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of ambient##2
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of pop##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
11. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| City      | berlin | boston | rome   | colone | nizza | liverpool     | miami |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | country  | hip-hop | classical     | d&b  | pop | dubstep |

