 5. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the ranch-style house is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the tower house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is the colonial house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
