 1. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the left of the person playing go##1
 4. the person playing go is the fan of techno##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 7. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 8. the fan of metal is between the fan of salsa and the person playing go##2
 9. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
11. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |   7    |
| Game   | whist         | billiard | canasta   | poker        | go  | backgammon  | domino |
| Music-Genre         | r&b | classical  | gospel | blues | techno | metal | salsa |

