.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, ebony, mauve, emerald, brown, red, chestnut
 1. the person who likes chestnut is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 4. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is between the person who likes brown and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 8. the person who likes red is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
11. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage           | sprite | coffee   | soy-milk | milk    | hot-chocolate   | 7up | iced-tea     |
| Color   | chestnut    | purple | emerald        | ebony | brown | red   | mauve |

 